  "title": "GENERAL MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Operations Management:</strong> Oversee daily, high-quality service operations, monitoring performance, and ensuring compliance with company policies and regulations.</li><li><strong>Customer & Service Excellence:</strong> Drive high standards of service, maintain client relationships, and address issues to ensure customer satisfaction.</li><li><strong>Financial Performance:</strong> Manage budgets, track expenses, analyze financial reports, and identify cost-saving measures to maximize profitability.</li><li><strong>Team Leadership & Staff Development:</strong> Recruit, train, motivate, and mentor staff, setting performance goals and conducting evaluations.</li><li><strong>Strategic Planning:</strong> Develop and execute strategies to improve operational efficiency, increase market share, and achieve organizational goals. </li></ul><p><strong>Required Skills and Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Leadership:</strong> Strong ability to lead teams and manage operational change.</li><li><strong>Communication:</strong> Excellent interpersonal skills to interact with staff, customers, and stakeholders.</li><li><strong>Financial Acumen:</strong> Proficiency in budgeting, forecasting, and financial analysis.</li><li><strong>Problem-Solving:</strong> Ability to handle crisis situations and make quick, effective decisions.</li><li><strong>Experience:</strong> Previous experience in management, specifically within a service-oriented industry.</li></ul>",
